🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure that accept any number from user and find number is even or odd.

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE check_even_odd(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
BEGIN
    IF n % 2 = 0 THEN
        RAISE NOTICE 'Even Number';
    ELSE
        RAISE NOTICE 'Odd Number';
    END IF;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

CALL check_even_odd(5);


